<!-- Field Guide:
- CATEGORY_TAGS: For filtering (e.g., "Builder,Consultant,Workshop")
- FULL_NAME: Person or company name
- SERVICE_TAGS_COMMA_SEPARATED: Display tags (e.g., "Rammed Earth,Cob,Training")
- SHORT_DESCRIPTION: One-line summary OR full description
- COUNTRY_NAME, CITY_NAME: Location
- LOCATIONS_IF_WORLDWIDE: Optional, show if serves multiple regions
- EMAIL: Email address
- PHONE_NUMBERS: Use format tel:+27214621614 (no spaces in href)
- PHONE_DISPLAY: What user sees (can include formatting/labels)
- WEBSITE_URL: Without http:// prefix
-->
